name: Johnny Numbnutz AI Artstyle
description:
Johnny_Numbnutz Style LoRA!


Making models can be time consuming and expensive. If you like what I do consider buying me a borgar🍔!

This artstyle is composed of bits of the helltaker style of artworks mixed with the OptionalTypo style. This adds a bit of depth to bodies, as well as intricacies to the color scheme of the helltaker style. This LORA is especially good at creating tomboy and nsfw artworks.

The trigger word for this LORA is johnny_numbnutz. I find a strength of 0.9-1.0 works the best for the intended output.

All pictures included are made using the hi-rez fix feature. Settings:
Denoising strength: 0.7,

Clip skip: 2,

Hires upscale: 2,

Hires steps: 50,

Hires upscaler: Latent
